snippet.title: Maui the Shapeshifter Reveal Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2024
snippet.description:
Revealed during the Future Games Show at Gamescom, Maui the Shapeshifter is an action platformer with a shapeshifting protagonist. It's coming soon to PC.
